[
  {
    "id": "thermal-tab",
    "type": "tab",
    "label": "Thermal Tanks",
    "disabled": false,
    "info": "Thermal tank Supervisor dashboard v0.4.1\n\nPOST endpoint:   /thermal/ingest  (pushed by the thermal-analyzer container)\nThermal API:     flow.thermal_base (default resolved from hostname, override with THERMAL_API)\n\nGroups:\n  \u2022 Overview       \u2014 site header + deep link to operator console (:8080)\n  \u2022 Live View      \u2014 MJPEG stream from the operator console (hostname auto-derived)\n  \u2022 Level Gauges   \u2014 one donut per tank\n  \u2022 Tanks          \u2014 per-tank KPI cards (level, ft, bbl, rate, ETA)\n  \u2022 Trends         \u2014 24 h level & temperature history (high-confidence only)\n  \u2022 Alerts         \u2014 persisted out-of-band history (bounded 200 rows)\n  \u2022 Events         \u2014 raw ingest log (collapsed)\n\nBreaking changes vs v0.3:\n  \u2022 `ts` is ALWAYS milliseconds (publisher guarantees). No unit math.\n  \u2022 Per-tank KPI cards replace the single ui_gauge (which collapsed multi-topic).\n  \u2022 Handles new payload fields: `reading`, `geometry`, `calibration`, `medium_confidence`, `site_id`.\n"
  },
